description=<SIZE:medium><LEFT><RGB:1,0.8,0.4>ZOMBIE VIRUS VACCINE [B42.13+ SP/MP] <LINE><LINE><LEFT><SIZE:small><RGB:0.9,0.9,0.9>Obviously, the logical solution to a zombie apocalypse is to set up a full laboratory in your backyard and start poking around in contaminated blood. <LINE><LEFT><SIZE:small>Build questionable equipment, perform autopsies with dubiously sourced tools, synthesize compounds that probably shouldn’t be anywhere near fire, and try to develop a cure before your closest volunteer decides to take a bite out of you. <LINE><LINE><LEFT><SIZE:small><RGB:1,0.35,0.25>DISCLAIMER: <LINE><LEFT><SIZE:small><RGB:0.6,1,0.8><SIZE:small><LEFT><RGB:1,0.8,0.4>I am not the original author of this mod — I only updated it for Build 42. <LINE><LEFT>After a full year since the unstable B42 release, I noticed that this mod was still unavailable. Personally, I consider it one of the best mods ever made, so I decided to update it myself. If the original author requests removal, I will take it down. For now, I intend to keep it updated as much as possible. <LINE><LINE><LEFT><RGB:1,0.35,0.25>DOES NOT REQUIRE PROFESSION MOD TO WORK!
